{"tid":2425320,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"拜登要求調查PS5同顯示卡晶片短缺嘅原因","createTime":"2021-02-27T09:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T10:37:34.000Z","uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a6f24efe9f3a2fdc13b09f45e723f37d6e09e60b","tid":2425320,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T09:30:37.000Z","msg":"President Biden Wants To 'Review' Cause Of PS5, Graphics Card Shortages<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kotaku.com/president-biden-wants-to-review-cause-of-ps5-graphics-1846349508?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkotaku.com%2Fpresident-biden-wants-to-review-cause-of-ps5-graphics-1846349508%3F&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm6npKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=1172a2d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://kotaku.com/president-biden-wants-to-review-cause-of-ps5-graphics-1846349508?</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_965/wsd6aruczz61xxvoum1y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kinja-img.com%2Fgawker-media%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fc_fit%2Cf_auto%2Cg_center%2Cpg_1%2Cq_60%2Cw_965%2Fwsd6aruczz61xxvoum1y.jpg&h=bf8c2c9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDon&rsquo;t eat it, Mr President! It&rsquo;s not that kind of chip!<br />\nPhoto: Pool (Getty Images)"},{"pid":"635c070f5ef1c603855eeb9b8d2ea4efd26ad157","tid":2425320,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T09:31:09.000Z","msg":"President Biden is getting ready to sign an executive order, one that will review the United States&rsquo; ability to get hold of certain things that it&rsquo;s currently having trouble getting hold of. On the list are semiconductors, one of the main reasons behind the current PS5 (and graphics card) shortages.<br />\n<br />\nAs CNBC reported earlier this month, a shortage of the chips&mdash;caused by pandemic interruptions to global supply chains&mdash;is wreaking havoc across the world, from car manufacturers to hardware companies like AMD and Qualcomm, and that&rsquo;s trickling on down to places like Sony and Nvidia, because you can&rsquo;t build PlayStations and GeForce cards without semiconductors.<br />\n<br />\nAP&rsquo;s report on the executive order says the review is targeting &ldquo;the fragility of vital supply chains,&rdquo; and will investigate whether&mdash;if a global situation makes it harder for the United States to import necessary components--the country needs to be manufacturing those things itself."},{"pid":"d67db0a0a2522b25469e3549abd3e905976a1de5","tid":2425320,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T09:31:21.000Z","msg":"It should be noted that this is an order to kick off a review, not to implement anything that it recommends. For all we know the President might get this review, say building more stuff in America is a good idea, then do nothing about it. Kinda like how he promised $2000 checks and hasn&rsquo;t done that either."},{"pid":"546c6e5341e14d78fc50ce2b9bf776a4ae6ec04a","tid":2425320,"uid":28114,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T09:32:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgur.com/CLjfH6p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FCLjfH6p.jpg&h=8ffd538a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來支那Joe都係機迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff8a8e57d3f0ae336eb4100d820cc227d182cc9","tid":2425320,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T09:36:07.000Z","msg":"btc<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\neth<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e11fed5a34d9b824bc90f0a71945dab6204b316","tid":2425320,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T09:37:22.000Z","msg":"呢下支持"},{"pid":"9dd6d04ee44e54d295c3ed05b6c92d80eb9c138c","tid":2425320,"uid":112748,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score